<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Help Center</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-alpha2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative; /* Set the position to relative */
        }
        form {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        /* Style for the floating button */
        .float-button {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="mt-3">Help Center</h1>

        <section>
            <h2>How to Register Your Vote?</h2>
            <p>To register your vote, follow these steps:
                <ol>
                    <li>Check your eligibility to vote.</li>
                    <li>Register on the online voting website "http://localhost:3000/register".</li>
                    <li>Submit the required details for verification.</li>
                    <li>Receive your voter ID card.</li>
                    <li>Find your polling station on the election day and cast your vote.</li>
                </ol>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Rules to Follow at Voting</h2>
            <p>When voting, please adhere to the following rules:
                <ul>
                    <li>Bring a valid ID card and your voter ID.</li>
                    <li>Do not campaign or wear political symbols near the polling station.</li>
                    <li>Follow the instructions of the polling officials.</li>
                    <li>Cast your vote in secret.</li>
                    <li>Do not influence or intimidate other voters.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Have Another Doubt?</h2>
            <p>If you have any other doubts or questions, please use the form below:</p>

            <form action="mailto:ggana6947@gmail.com" method="post" enctype="text/plain">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Your Email:</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="doubt" class="form-label">Your Doubt:</label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="doubt" name="doubt" rows="4" required></textarea>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and Popper.js -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.10.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-alpha2/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Back to Dashboard floating button -->
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary float-button">Back to Dashboard</a>

</body>
</html>
